reviewText: One of the most boring documentaries I've ever had the misfortune of watching.  This was a huge waste of time AND money. Sorry, I wish I could make at least one positive comment.

Great naturist video. Pretty decent video quality, not as good as the Naturist Freedom videos but good. It is about families enjoying the sun in a nudist setting. Males and females of all ages are represented. I seen the movie listed in a new release book on Amazon.com titled The First Guide To Girls In Nudist Videos.
I enjoyed this film and recomend this to anyone who appreciates nudism. A russian family enjoying the beach playing in the water and dirt?
